title: Grammys 2017: Vote for the Best and Worst Dressed
text: Pin it Share The Grammys ’ red carpet isn’t your typical celebrity fashion show. Historically, the dress code has been: The crazier the better. But being best dressed is still the highest honor. How’s it decided who gets that honor — and the ill-fated worst dressed too? It’s all up to you! Vote on what everyone’s wearing on the red carpet tonight. Their fate is in your fingers — and don’t forget to comment below! Adele in Givenchy Haute Couture.
